				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$(|\eta |\ge 1.5)$$\end{document} in order to improve the quality of the selected tracks. The fake-vertex rate is also better controlled by limiting the algorithm to only consider the 25 highest-pT\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
