The light-flavour jet rejection as a function of b-jet rejection for inclusive 20%, 30%, and 40% c-jet efficiency operating points for the DL1 and DL1r high-level c-taggers. Each point on a curve corresponds to a particular choice of fb,\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
