In order to correct the tagging rates of jets in simulation, corresponding rates are measured in data through a variety of procedures [6, 53–56], reaching a precision as good as 1% in b-tagging efficiency for b-jets with pT∼100\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
